> Click and Mouse Actions:

  Single Click:
  - Selenium: click()
  - Playwright: click()

  Double Click:
  - Selenium: ActionChains.double_click(element).perform()
  - Playwright: dblclick()

  Right Click (Context Click):
  - Selenium: ActionChains.context_click(element).perform()
  - Playwright: click(button='right')

  Hover:
  - Selenium: ActionChains.move_to_element(element).perform()
  - Playwright: hover()

  Drag and Drop:
  - Selenium: ActionChains.drag_and_drop(source, target).perform()
  - Playwright: drag_and_drop(source, target)
